or 12. For her, the war was about to begin. ; Photo, Le Ly's mother, Tran Thi 
Quen, left, and her father, Phung Van Trong, in 1962. ; Photo, Le Ly's older 
brother Bon Nghe, left, and Le Ly, standing, at 17, with a niece in Da Nang. ; 
Photo, Le Ly with her first husband, Ed Munro, in 1971. 
</P>
