</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Work has started on the four-story, $15 million Watt Pacifica Plaza office 
building at the northwest corner of Barranca Parkway and Pacifica Street in the 
Irvine Spectrum business complex. 
</P>
