<HEADLINE>
<P>
$10,000 FOR QUAKE RELIEF 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
MONTEBELLO 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Beverly Hospital board of directors has donated $10,000 in lieu of medical 
supplies to the Armenian earthquake relief effort. The donation was made 
through the Hospital Council of Southern California. 
</P>
</TEXT>
