<P>
DIRECTOR GUILD OF AMERICA; MOTION PICTURES; AWARDS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA020589-0187 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 14702 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
February 5, 1989, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
