</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA020589-0220 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 14982 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
February 5, 1989, Sunday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part 2; Page 2; Column 5; Metro Desk 
</P>
