<HEADLINE>
<P>
FRESHMAN ANTON LIFTS BREA-OLINDA 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Freshman Jody Anton made two free throws with 4 seconds remaining to give 
Brea-Olinda a 64-63 victory over Buena of Ventura in girls' basketball Saturday 
at Buena. 
</P>
<P>
The Wildcats trailed, 59-52, with 2 minutes left before going on a 12-4 run. 
</P>
<P>
Allison Bickel's 15-footer made the score 63-62 with 48 seconds left before 
Tammy Blackburn stole the ball to set up Anton's free throws. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Game Story 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
